tasks in proof planning.- Using charts for transfer in MT.- A new frame for common-sense reasoning - Towards local inconsistencies.- Prioritized transitions for updates.- An optimal bidirectional search algorithm.- Learning to discriminate phases in gas-liquid flow.- Strategies for semantical contractions.- Conflicts in the spatial interaction of autonomous agents.- Using rough sets theory to predict German word stress.- Graphtheoretical algorithms and knowledge-based design.- Interval situation calculus.},
